definitions.definition: Something which is not genuine , or is presented fraudulently .
examples: I suspect this passport is a fake .

definitions.definition: ( sports ) A move meant to deceive an opposing player, used for gaining advantage for example when dribbling an opponent.

main_definition: Something which is not genuine , or is presented fraudulently .
secondary_definitions: ( sports ) A move meant to deceive an opposing player, used for gaining advantage for example when dribbling an opponent.

definitions.definition: One of the circles or windings of a cable or hawser , as it lies in a coil ; a single turn or coil.

main_definition: ( nautical ) One of the circles or windings of a cable or hawser , as it lies in a coil ; a single turn or coil.
